primary.detail: The caller played a recording or spoke a message that sounded like an IVR message and then disconnected.

steps: User provided a recorded message instead of a request.
Agent attempted to re-engage and the call ended.

failure.detail: The caller appears to be another automated system or played a recording, preventing a real interaction.

insights.summary: The call was abandoned before a request was made; the user turn contained a recorded message about no one being available.
insights.verbatim: It seems like no one is available to take your call at the moment.
